<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>فَصْلٌ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">تُسَنُّ العَقِيقَةُ:</span> عَنِ الغُلَامِ شَاتَانِ، وَعَنِ الجَارِيَةِ شَاةٌ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>تُذْبَحُ يَوْمَ سَابِعِهِ،<span class="c5"> فَإِنْ فَاتَ:</span> فَفِي أَرْبَعَةَ عَشَرَ،<span class="c5"> فَإِنْ فَاتَ:</span> فَفِي إِحْدَى وَعِشْرِينَ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وتُنْزَعُ جُدُولاً، وَلَا يُكْسَرُ عَظْمُهَا.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">وَحُكْمُهَا:</span> كَالأُضْحِيَةِ؛ إِلَّا أَنَّهُ لَا يُجْزِئُ فِيهَا شِرْكٌ فِي دَمٍ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَلَا تُسَنُّ الفَرَعَةُ، وَلَا العَتِيرَةُ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>* * *<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>